e","msrp":"68.0","name":"Silk and Lace Camisole","retail_price":"54.99","short_description":"A luxurious silk camisole adorned with intricate lace trim, perfect for sleep or elegant layering.","size":"Medium","sku":"199902","sub_category":"Top","upc":"850062451893"},{"alt_text":"Front view of charcoal gray fleece jogger sweatpants with a drawstring waist and elastic cuffs.","brand":"Volt","category":"Apparel","collection":"Core Activewear","color_hex":"#5A5A5A","color_name":"Charcoal Gray","cost":"21.5","department":"Unisex","fit_type":"Regular","image_uri":"https://storage.googleapis.com/YOUR_PROJECT_ID-artifacts/products/583944.png","long_description":"Stay comfortable and stylish with our Unisex Fleece Jogger Sweatpants. Made from a soft and warm fleece material, these pants are perfect for lounging, working out, or running errands. They feature an adjustable drawstring for a custom fit, convenient side pockets, and elastic-cuffed ankles for a modern jogger silhouette. The classic charcoal gray color makes them a versatile addition to any casual wardrobe.","material":"Fleece","msrp":"55.0","name":"Unisex Fleece Jogger Sweatpants","retail_price":"45.99","short_description":"Classic fleece jogger sweatpants in a versatile charcoal gray, featuring a comfortable drawstring waist and cuffed ankles.","size":"Medium","sku":"583944","sub_category":"Bottom","upc":"840350112345"},{"alt_text":"A black and cream checkered v-neck knit sweater vest laid flat on a white surface.","brand":"Modern Muse","category":"Apparel","collection":"Fall/Winter 2023","color_hex":"#F5F5DC","color_name":"Black/Cream","cost":"35.0","department":"Unisex","fit_type":"Regular Fit","image_uri":"https://storage.googleapis.com/YOUR_PROJECT_ID-artifacts/products/239944.png","long_description":"Stay warm and stylish with this timeless checkered knit sweater vest. Crafted from a soft, comfortable knit fabric, it features a classic v-neckline and ribbed trim along the neck, armholes, and hem. The striking black and cream checkerboard pattern makes a statement, offering a versatile piece that can be dressed up or down. Layer it over a crisp white shirt for a preppy look or a simple t-shirt for a more casual vibe.","material":"Wool Blend","msrp":"85.0","name":"Checkered Knit Sweater Vest","retail_price":"70.0","short_description":"A classic v-neck sweater vest featuring a bold black and cream checkerboard pattern, perfect for layering.","size":"Medium","sku":"239944","sub_category":"Top","upc":"850024681357"},{"alt_text":"Women's long-sleeve collared shirtdress in a cream and grey geometric pattern with a matching belt.","brand":"Modern Muse","category":"Apparel","collection":"Modern Elegance","color_hex":"#F3EFE9","color_name":"Cream/Grey","cost":"135.0","department":"Women","fit_type":"Regular Fit","image_uri":"https://storage.googleapis.com/YOUR_PROJECT_ID-artifacts/products/192844.png","long_description":"This elegant shirtdress is designed for a timeless appeal. It's crafted from a fluid satin fabric that drapes beautifully. The dress features a classic point collar, a full button-down front, and long sleeves with cuffed ends. A bold geometric print covers the entirety of the dress, offering a modern, graphic look. A matching fabric belt allows you to define your silhouette. The knee-length cut and curved hem make it a versatile piece for both professional settings and special occasions.","material":"Satin","msrp":"325.0","name":"Geometric Print Satin Shirtdress","retail_price":"275.0","short_description":"A sophisticated long-sleeve shirtdress crafted from smooth satin, featuring a striking geometric print and a self-tie belt to cinch the waist.","size":"Medium","sku":"192844","sub_category":"Dress","upc":"840348192844"},{"alt_text":"Front view of an emerald green satin long-sleeve blouse with a high mock neck and button details.","brand":"Modern Muse","category":"Apparel","collection":"Evening Elegance","color_hex":"#00573D","color_name":"Emerald Green","cost"