ntial. Made from a soft cotton-blend fabric, it features a relaxed fit for easy layering and all-day comfort. The design includes a classic adjustable drawstring hood, a spacious front kangaroo pocket, and ribbed cuffs and hem to lock in warmth. A tonal embroidered logo on the chest adds a subtle, premium touch to this minimalist piece.","material":"Cotton Blend","msrp":"110.0","name":"Relaxed Fit Embroidered Hoodie","retail_price":"110.0","short_description":"A comfortable, relaxed-fit hoodie in a versatile beige color, featuring a drawstring hood, kangaroo pocket, and subtle tonal embroidery on the chest.","size":"Medium","sku":"667734","sub_category":"Top","upc":"198765432109"},{"alt_text":"White and black tweed sleeveless mini dress with button details.","brand":"Maison Onyx","category":"Apparel","collection":"Classic Collection","color_hex":"#F5F5F5","color_name":"White/Black","cost":"180.0","department":"Women","fit_type":"Sheath","image_uri":"https://storage.googleapis.com/YOUR_PROJECT_ID-artifacts/products/982349.png","long_description":"Embody Parisian chic with this exquisite sleeveless mini dress. Meticulously crafted from a luxurious white and black tweed fabric, this piece showcases the brand's iconic aesthetic. It features a flattering sheath silhouette, a round neckline, and contrasting black trim along the neck, armholes, waist, pockets, and hem. Ornate silver-tone buttons adorn the faux chest pockets, hip pockets, and shoulders, adding a touch of opulence. This dress is a perfect choice for sophisticated day-to-evening wear.","material":"Tweed","msrp":"495.0","name":"Tweed Sleeveless Mini Dress","retail_price":"450.0","short_description":"A timeless sleeveless mini dress crafted from classic tweed, featuring contrasting black trim and elegant button embellishments.","size":"Medium","sku":"982349","sub_category":"Dress","upc":"196924009823"},{"alt_text":"A short-sleeved tweed mini dress in black and white with embellished trim along the crew neck, cuffs, waist, and faux pocket details.","brand":"Maison Onyx","category":"Apparel","collection":"Fall/Winter 2023","color_hex":"#FFFFFF","color_name":"Black/White Multi","cost":"312.75","department":"Women","fit_type":"Sheath","image_uri":"https://storage.googleapis.com/YOUR_PROJECT_ID-artifacts/products/343485.png","long_description":"Exude timeless elegance with this Embellished Tweed Sheath Dress. Expertly tailored from a rich, textured tweed fabric, this piece showcases a sophisticated black and white pattern interwoven with subtle metallic threads for a hint of shimmer. The dress is designed in a flattering sheath silhouette that hugs the body gracefully. It features a classic crew neckline, short sleeves, and is accented with intricate beaded and frayed trim along the collar, cuffs, defined waistline, and hem. This dress is a perfect choice for formal events, business meetings, or any occasion where you want to make a chic statement.","material":"Tweed","msrp":"495.0","name":"Embellished Tweed Sheath Dress","retail_price":"450.0","short_description":"A beautifully crafted tweed mini dress featuring a black and white pattern with sparkling embellishments. This sheath dress has a classic crew neck and short sleeves, perfect for a sophisticated and polished look.","size":"Medium","sku":"343485","sub_category":"Dress","upc":"840345123456"},{"alt_text":"Sleeveless black sheath dress with a pearl-embellished jewel neckline, front view.","brand":"Maison Onyx","category":"Apparel","collection":"Cocktail & Evening Collection","color_hex":"#000000","color_name":"Black","cost":"85.5","department":"Women","fit_type":"Sheath Fit","image_uri":"https://storage.googleapis.com/YOUR_PROJECT_ID-artifacts/products/119283.png","long_description":"Exude timeless sophistication in our Pearl-Collar Sleeveless Sheath Dress. Tailored to perfection, this classic black dress features a flattering sheath silhouette that skims the body beautifully. The standout detail is the exquisite pearl-embellished jewel neckline, adding a touch of luxury and eliminating the need for a necklace. Crafted from a high-quality crepe fabric with a hint of stretch for comfort, it's fully lined and fastens with a concealed back zipper. A versatile and chic addition to any wardrobe, this dress is ideal for cocktail hours, weddings, or any formal occasion where you want to make a lasting impression.","material":"Crepe","msrp":"198.0","name":"Pearl-Collar Sleeveless Sheath Dress","retail_price":"179.99","short_description":"An elegant sleeveless black sheath dress featuring a sophisticated pearl-embellished jewel neckline. Perfect for formal events and cocktail parties.","size":"Medium","sku":"119283","sub_category":"Dress","upc":"850051234567"},{"alt_text":"A sleeveless cream tweed mini dress with black contrast trim on the neckline, armholes, and four front patch pockets with silver buttons.","brand":"Modern Muse","category":"Apparel","collection":"Pre-Fall 2023","color_hex":"#F5F5DC","color_name":"Cream/Black","cost":"198.75","department":"Women","fit_type":"Shift","image_uri":"https://storage.googleapis.com/YOUR_PROJECT_ID-artifacts/products/192838.png","long_description":"This beautifully constructed shift dress channels classic Parisian elegance. Made from a high-quality cream-colored tweed, it offers both texture and structure. The sleeveless design is complemented by bold black trim along the round neck and armholes. Four patch pockets, two at the chest and two at the hips, are also accented with black trim and finished with ornate silver-tone buttons. A concealed back zipper provides a clean, tailored fit. This versatile piece is perfect for transitioning from a daytime meeting to an evening event with effortless style.","material":"Tweed","msrp":"445.0","name":"Sleeveless Tweed Mini Dress with Contrast Trim","retail_price":"445.0","short_description":"A timelessly chic sleeveless mini dress crafted from textured tweed, featuring elegant black contrast trim and four