","name":"Faux Leather Straight-Leg Pants","retail_price":"79.99","short_description":"Sleek and modern faux leather pants with a classic straight-leg cut and five-pocket styling.","size":"Medium","sku":"234444","sub_category":"Bottom","upc":"840348123456"},{"alt_text":"Front view of women's high-waisted wide-leg trousers in a black and white houndstooth pattern.","brand":"Modern Muse","category":"Apparel","collection":"Autumn Classics","color_hex":"#000000","color_name":"Black/White Houndstooth","cost":"45.5","department":"Women","fit_type":"Wide-Leg","image_uri":"https://storage.googleapis.com/YOUR_PROJECT_ID-artifacts/products/839185.png","long_description":"Elevate your wardrobe with these sophisticated High-Waisted Houndstooth Trousers. Expertly tailored from a quality wool-blend fabric, they offer both structure and comfort. The classic black and white houndstooth print provides a timeless appeal, while the high-waisted design and front pleats create a flattering shape. A relaxed, wide-leg cut ensures ease of movement and a chic, flowing silhouette. These trousers are a versatile addition, perfect for transitioning from a professional office setting to an elegant evening out.","material":"Wool Blend","msrp":"128.0","name":"High-Waisted Houndstooth Trousers","retail_price":"99.99","short_description":"Classic high-waisted trousers featuring a timeless black and white houndstooth pattern and a modern wide-leg silhouette.","size":"Medium","sku":"839185","sub_category":"Bottom","upc":"198765432109"},{"alt_text":"Front view of women's oatmeal colored high-waisted pleated wide-leg culottes with a single button closure.","brand":"Modern Muse","category":"Apparel","collection":"Modern Essentials","color_hex":"#EAE3D5","color_name":"Oatmeal","cost":"95.5","department":"Women","fit_type":"Wide-Leg","image_uri":"https://storage.googleapis.com/YOUR_PROJECT_ID-artifacts/products/294832.png","long_description":"Elevate your wardrobe with our High-Waisted Pleated Culottes. Expertly tailored from a structured wool-blend fabric, they sit comfortably at the natural waist and flow into a graceful, wide-leg shape that ends at a cropped length. The crisp front pleats add volume and movement, creating a polished and contemporary look. These versatile trousers are perfect for transitioning from the office to an evening out, offering both comfort and impeccable style.","material":"Wool Blend","msrp":"225.0","name":"High-Waisted Pleated Culottes","retail_price":"198.0","short_description":"Sophisticated and modern, these high-waisted culottes feature sharp pleats and a flattering wide-leg silhouette.","size":"Medium","sku":"294832","sub_category":"Bottom","upc":"840351829457"},{"alt_text":"Front view of a women's navy blue satin jacquard long-sleeve wrap midi dress on a white background.","brand":"Maison Onyx","category":"Apparel","collection":"Evening Elegance","color_hex":"#19213D","color_name":"Navy Blue","cost":"150.0","department":"Women","fit_type":"Wrap","image_uri":"https://storage.googleapis.com/YOUR_PROJECT_ID-artifacts/products/293852.png","long_description":"Crafted from a luxurious satin jacquard fabric with a subtle polka dot pattern, this wrap dress exudes timeless elegance. It's designed with a classic V-neckline, voluminous long bishop sleeves with cuffed wrists, and a self-tie belt to cinch the waist for a defined silhouette. The flowing midi-length skirt creates beautiful movement, making it perfect for special occasions, cocktail parties, or formal dinners. The wrap design ensures a comfortable and adjustable fit for effortless sophistication.","material":"Satin Jacquard","msrp":"350.0","name":"Satin Jacquard Wrap Midi Dress","retail_price":"325.0","short_description":"Elevate your evening look with this stunning navy blue satin jacquard wrap dress, featuring long bishop sleeves and a flattering midi length.","size":"Medium","sku":"293852","sub_category":"Dress","upc":"850024987123"},{"alt_text":"A side view of a retro-style 